# 25 - Dependency Auditor
# Analyze project dependencies

NAME dep-audit
INPUT manifest_file
INPUT ecosystem DEFAULT "auto-detect"

GOAL parse "Read $manifest_file. List dependencies with versions. Detect $ecosystem if needed."
GOAL analyze "Check dependencies for known issues using existing knowledge. Max 1-2 web searches only for specific CVE lookups if critical."
GOAL recommend "Prioritized recommendations: critical vulnerabilities first, then outdated, then maintenance concerns. Top 5-10 items."
GOAL report "Concise health report with prioritized action items. Save to dep-audit-output.md."

RUN audit USING parse, analyze, recommend, report
